Hydras:

"Then we will face it" muttered hydras "Cyclonus Rise the defences, and put 
them in the max!!!!! wait my signal to destroy anything that is around our 
perimeter!!!! Take the minimal bots to keep repairs going !!!  The est of 
them must follow me!!!!"

Hydras headed towards the exit

-----Original Message----- 
From: Super Cyclonus
Sent: Monday, July 11, 2011 6:00 AM
To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com
Subject: Re: Hydras and Predacons

> <OLD>
>
> Hydras hissed and said "Keep working. Tell me when the repairs are done"

<NEW>

There was a nod from CYCLONUS, his optics glittering thoughtfully. "Of
course sir. However with the exception of your quarters and a few
other small sections of the ship we are largely done. We cannot get
the ship to fly without a new fuel flow regulator, but everything ese
is in readiness."

There is a beep as CYCLONUS and HYDRAS get a message from SCOURGE who
is manning the sensors and security station on the bridge. "We are
picking up something strange, and I am not sure of what to make of it.
It looks like a large herd of reptiles of all sorts moving across the
open plains."

There was a pause from SCOURGE for a moment and then he continued, "I
have a sweep watching it now from a distance and it is massive.
Herbavores, carnivores, omnivores all running together." There was
another pause from SCOURGE, as if this next part confused him. "Above
them is floating a strange . . . I don't know . . . From what the
sweep reports it looks like a dinobot but it registers as a both
Predacon and Decepticon. We can't explain it."

(TAG)

Preston
